snippet.title: RC Revenge Pro - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is the enhanced PS2 version of RC Revenge, a sequel to Re-Volt. And much like Re-Volt, it is just as hard and chaotic, regardless whether it's the OG PSone version or the PS2 version.

RC Revenge, RC Revenge Pro, Re-Volt (C) SuperDay
Originally from Acclaim Entertainment
Captured from the actual PS2 console
